---
title: Sticky Plum, Mushroom & Chicken Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: Double mushrooms equals double the fun at dinner time. Stir-fry them up in a sticky and sweet plum soy sauce to crank the
excitement up to ten and add some garlic aromas to the rice and your tastebuds will have the time of their life tonight.
